# Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy applies to haploop (hereafter referred to as the "Application"), provided by Takashi Tanaka. The Application is offered free of charge and is intended for use "as is."

## Information Collected and Its Use

The Application does not collect any information when downloaded or used. No registration is required to use the Application. Data is collected only when you contact Takashi Tanaka via email, and only the information you share in your email is sent or collected.

## Does the Application Collect Real-Time Location Information?

The Application does not collect precise real-time location information from your device.

## Do Third Parties Access Information Collected by the Application?

Since the Application does not collect any information, no data is shared with third parties.

## Opt-Out Rights

As no data is collected, there is no need to opt-out.

## Children's Privacy

The Application is not intended for use in collecting data from or marketing to children under the age of 13.

Takashi Tanaka does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13. Additionally, all children are advised not to submit personally identifiable information through the Application or related services. Parents and legal guardians are encouraged to monitor their children's internet usage and instruct them to comply with this Policy.

## Security

Takashi Tanaka is committed to safeguarding the confidentiality of your information. However, as the Application does not collect any data, there is no risk of data breaches or unauthorized access.

## Changes

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time as needed. Any changes to the Privacy Policy will be notified by publishing the updated policy on this page. Please review this Policy regularly. Continued use of the Application signifies acceptance of all changes.

This Privacy Policy is effective as of January 22, 2025.

## Consent

By using the Application, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy and any future updates.

## Contact

If you have any questions about privacy while using the Application or any concerns regarding this Policy, please contact Takashi Tanaka at the following email address:

- **Email**: takashi.tanaka.design@gmail.com